72: ## 2. Islands Architecture & Partial Hydration <a name="islands-architecture"></a>
73: 
74: ### The Island Concept
75: 
76: ```
77: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
78: │                    Page (Static HTML)                  │
79: │                                                        │
80: │  ┌──────────────┐   ┌──────────────────────────────┐  │
81: │  │   Header     │   │                              │  │
82: │  │  (Static)    │   │     Terminal Component       │  │
83: │  │  No JS ✨    │   │     (React Island)           │  │
84: │  └──────────────┘   │     JS loaded ⚡             │  │
85: │                      │                              │  │
86: │  ┌──────────────┐   │     - xterm.js               │  │
87: │  │   About      │   │     - Command handling       │  │
88: │  │  (Static)    │   │     - Keyboard events        │  │
89: │  │  No JS ✨    │   │                              │  │
90: │  └──────────────┘   └──────────────────────────────┘  │
91: │                                                        │
92: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │
93: │  │              Footer (Static) — No JS ✨           │  │
94: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │
95: └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
96: ```
97: 
98: Only the Terminal component ships JavaScript. Everything else is pure HTML/CSS.
99: 
100: ### Hydration Directives
101: 
102: Astro provides several directives to control *when* an island's JavaScript loads:
103: 
104: | Directive | When JS Loads | Use Case |
105: |-----------|--------------|----------|
106: | `client:load` | Immediately on page load | Critical interactive elements |
107: | `client:idle` | When browser is idle | Non-critical widgets |
108: | `client:visible` | When element scrolls into view | Below-fold components |
109: | `client:media="(max-width: 768px)"` | When media query matches | Mobile-only interactivity |
110: | `client:only="react"` | Client-only (no SSR) | Components using browser APIs |
111: 
112: ```astro
113: ---
114: // src/pages/index.astro
115: import Terminal from '../components/Terminal.tsx';
116: import Analytics from '../components/Analytics.tsx';
117: import MobileMenu from '../components/MobileMenu.tsx';
118: ---
119: 
120: <!-- Loads JS immediately — terminal must work on page load -->
121: <Terminal client:load />
122: 
123: <!-- Loads JS when browser is idle — not critical -->
124: <Analytics client:idle />
125: 
126: <!-- Only loads on mobile viewports -->
127: <MobileMenu client:media="(max-width: 768px)" />
128: ```
